name book-of-common-prayer
category Package
revision 59742
shortdesc Typeset in the style of "Book of Common Prayer"
longdesc This a package for the typesetting of liturgical documents in
longdesc the style of the 1979 "Book of Common Prayer". It provides
longdesc macros for common liturgical situations (e.g. versicle and
longdesc response, longer prayers, etc.). This package is designed to
longdesc work with the Sabon font, but it is not necessary to run the
longdesc macros.
